svt_axi_slave_base_sequence Class Reference

Inheritance diagram for class svt_axi_slave_base_sequence:

List of all members.

Detailed Description

This sequence raises/drops objections in the pre/post_body so that root sequences raise objections but subsequences do not. All other slave sequences in the collection extend from this base sequence.

Execution phase: run_phase Sequencer: Slave agent sequencer

 int  attribute
 svt_axi_slave_base_sequence::update_memory_in_request_order = 0

Field for updating slave memory in request order. This can be configured by the user. Default value is 0. When set to 1, updates slave memory in request order.
